This paper focuses on the security and efficiency of multitasking within a single enclave of Intel SGX. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), operating systems (cs.OS), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and architecture (cs.AR).
